    "source_target": "third_party/curvytron-reference",
    "source_commit": "8fec14c",
    "notes": [
      "JS lifecycle oracle proof for source Game.removeAvatar() after round:end and before game:stop in a three-player round.",
      "The harness starts a real source round, waits for delayed PrintManager.start timers, forces avatars 3 and 2 into same-frame wall deaths so avatar 1 wins, then removes avatar 1 during warmdown.",
      "It proves the warmdown leave emits die/stop/player:leave side effects without re-scoring, without emitting a second round:end, and without changing the current Game.deaths collection.",
      "At game:stop the source resizes the arena to the two still-present players, starts a next round, and the non-present leaver is placed in deaths by onRoundNew()."
    ]
  },
